name: Felix the Goat 2.0
description:
Felix landed on “earth” totally confused with what he saw… on one side , a dark side , the “money man in suit” destroying piece by piece this beautiful planet … on the other side , a clear sky, and a angel spreading love over this unique nature. 
He is feeling a strange mix between choosing the greediness for money and fame or help to spread love for nature.
Confused Felix.
